title: Kate and Anna McGarrigle 1977-02-03 Rockpalast, Studio L, WDR
description:
Here is a nice bootleg. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)

Kate & Anna McGarrigle

1977-02-03 Rockpalast, WDR Studio-L, Cologne, West Germany (MKV) + interview (FLAC)

Reds are well oversaturated on this transfer from Betamax tape, but overall the picture has far more punch and contrast than the washed out quality of the DVD already circulating.
